msgid "# Service Profiling Guide"
msgstr "# 服务性能分析指南"

msgid ""
"In an inference service process, it is sometimes necessary to monitor the "
"internal execution flow of the inference service framework to identify "
"performance issues. By collecting start and end timestamps of key processes,"
" identifying key functions or iterations, recording critical events, and "
"gathering various types of information, performance bottlenecks can be "
"quickly located."
msgstr ""
"在推理服务过程中，有时需要监控推理服务框架的内部执行流程，以识别性能问题。通过收集关键流程的开始和结束时间戳、识别关键函数或迭代、记录关键事件以及收集各类信息，可以快速定位性能瓶颈。"

msgid ""
"This guide will walk you through the process of collecting performance data "
"from the vLLM-Ascend service framework and operators. It covers the complete"
" workflow from preparation, collection, analysis, to visualization, helping "
"you quickly get started with performance collection tools."
msgstr ""
"本指南将引导您完成从 vLLM-Ascend "
"服务框架和算子中收集性能数据的过程。它涵盖了从准备、收集、分析到可视化的完整工作流程，帮助您快速上手性能收集工具。"

msgid ""
"Two performance collection solutions are provided below: Ascend PyTorch "
"Profiler and MS Service Profiler. You can choose the appropriate tool for "
"performance analysis and troubleshooting based on your actual requirements."
msgstr ""
"下面提供两种性能收集方案：Ascend PyTorch Profiler 和 MS Service "
"Profiler。您可以根据实际需求选择合适的工具进行性能分析和问题排查。"

msgid "## Solution Comparison"
msgstr "## 方案对比"

msgid "## Quick Selection Guide"
msgstr "## 快速选择指南"

msgid ""
"- [**Model Operator Performance** → Use Ascend PyTorch Profiler](#ascend-pytorch-profiler)\n"
"- [**Service Framework Workflow** → Use MS Service Profiler](#ms-service-profiler)"
msgstr ""
"- [**模型算子性能** → 使用 Ascend PyTorch Profiler](#ascend-pytorch-profiler)\n"
"- [**服务框架工作流** → 使用 MS Service Profiler](#ms-service-profiler)"

msgid "## MS Service Profiler"
msgstr "## MS Service Profiler"

msgid "### 0. Build from Source and Upgrade"
msgstr "### 0. 从源码构建并升级"

msgid ""
"The `msserviceprofiler` tool is pre-installed with the CANN Toolkit package."
" Use the following commands to install or upgrade from source."
msgstr "`msserviceprofiler` 工具随 CANN Toolkit 包预装。使用以下命令从源码安装或升级。"

msgid "### 1. Preparation"
msgstr "### 1. 准备工作"

msgid ""
"Before starting the service, set the environment variable "
"`SERVICE_PROF_CONFIG_PATH` to point to the profiling configuration file, and"
" set the environment variable `PROFILING_SYMBOLS_PATH` to specify the YAML "
"configuration file for the symbols that need to be imported. After that, "
"start the vLLM service according to your deployment method."
msgstr ""
"在启动服务前，设置环境变量 `SERVICE_PROF_CONFIG_PATH` 指向性能分析配置文件，并设置环境变量 "
"`PROFILING_SYMBOLS_PATH` 指定需要导入的符号的 YAML 配置文件。之后，根据您的部署方式启动 vLLM 服务。"

msgid ""
"The file `ms_service_profiler_config.json` is the profiling configuration. "
"If it does not exist at the specified path, a default configuration will be "
"generated automatically. If needed, you can customize it in advance "
"according to the instructions in the `Profiling Configuration File` section "
"below."
msgstr ""
"文件 `ms_service_profiler_config.json` "
"是性能分析配置文件。如果指定路径下不存在该文件，将自动生成默认配置。如有需要，您可以根据下方`性能分析配置文件`部分的说明提前自定义配置。"

msgid ""
"`service_profiling_symbols.yaml` is the configuration file containing the "
"profiling points to be imported. You can choose **not** to set the "
"`PROFILING_SYMBOLS_PATH` environment variable, in which case the default "
"configuration file will be used. If the file does not exist at the path you "
"specified, likewise, the system will generate a configuration file at your "
"specified path for future configuration. You can customize it according to "
"the instructions in the `Symbols Configuration File` section below."
msgstr ""
"`service_profiling_symbols.yaml` 是包含待导入性能分析点的配置文件。您可以选择**不**设置 "
"`PROFILING_SYMBOLS_PATH` "
"环境变量，此时将使用默认配置文件。如果文件在您指定的路径下不存在，系统同样会在您指定的路径生成一个配置文件供后续配置。您可以根据下方`符号配置文件`部分的说明进行自定义。"

msgid "### 2. Enable Profiling"
msgstr "### 2. 启用性能分析"

msgid ""
"To enable the performance data collection switch, change the `enable` field "
"from `0` to `1` in the configuration file `ms_service_profiler_config.json`."
" This can be accomplished by executing the following sed command:"
msgstr ""
"要启用性能数据采集开关，请将配置文件 `ms_service_profiler_config.json` 中的 `enable` 字段从 `0` 改为 "
"`1`。这可以通过执行以下 sed 命令来完成："

msgid "### 3. Send Requests"
msgstr "### 3. 发送请求"

msgid ""
"Choose a request-sending method that suits your actual profiling needs:"
msgstr "选择适合您实际性能分析需求的请求发送方式："

msgid "### 4. Parse Data"
msgstr "### 4. 解析数据"

msgid "### 5. View Results"
msgstr "### 5. 查看结果"

msgid "After parsing, the `output` directory will contain:"
msgstr "解析后，`output` 目录将包含："

msgid ""
"- `chrome_tracing.json`: Chrome tracing format data, which can be opened in [MindStudio Insight](https://www.hiascend.com/document/detail/zh/mindstudio/830/GUI_baseddevelopmenttool/msascendinsightug/Insight_userguide_0002.html?framework=mindspore).\n"
"- `profiler.db`: Performance data in database format.\n"
"- `request.csv`: Request-related data.\n"
"- `kvcache.csv`: KV Cache-related data.\n"
"- `batch.csv`: Batch scheduling-related data."
msgstr ""
"- `chrome_tracing.json`：Chrome tracing 格式数据，可在 [MindStudio Insight](https://www.hiascend.com/document/detail/zh/mindstudio/830/GUI_baseddevelopmenttool/msascendinsightug/Insight_userguide_0002.html?framework=mindspore) 中打开。\n"
"- `profiler.db`：数据库格式的性能数据。\n"
"- `request.csv`：请求相关数据。\n"
"- `kvcache.csv`：KV Cache 相关数据。\n"
"- `batch.csv`：批量调度相关数据。"

msgid "### 6. Appendix related to MS Service Profiler"
msgstr "### 6. MS Service Profiler 相关附录"

msgid "(profiling-configuration-file)="
msgstr "(profiling-configuration-file)="

msgid "#### 6.1 Profiling Configuration File"
msgstr "#### 6.1 性能分析配置文件"

msgid ""
"The profiling configuration file controls profiling parameters and behavior."
msgstr "性能分析配置文件控制性能分析参数和行为。"

msgid "##### File Format"
msgstr "##### 文件格式"

msgid "The configuration is in JSON format. Main parameters:"
msgstr "配置采用 JSON 格式。主要参数："

msgid "##### Example Configuration"
msgstr "##### 配置示例"

msgid "(symbols-configuration-file)="
msgstr "(symbols-configuration-file)="

msgid "#### 6.2 Symbols Configuration File"
msgstr "#### 6.2 符号配置文件"

msgid ""
"The symbols configuration file defines which functions/methods to profile "
"and supports flexible configuration with custom attribute collection."
msgstr "符号配置文件定义了要分析哪些函数/方法，并支持通过自定义属性收集进行灵活配置。"

msgid "##### File Name and Loading"
msgstr "##### 文件名与加载"

msgid ""
"- Default load "
"path:`~/.config/vllm_ascend/service_profiling_symbols.MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH.yaml`("
" According to the installed version of vllm )"
msgstr ""
"- "
"默认加载路径：`~/.config/vllm_ascend/service_profiling_symbols.MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH.yaml`（根据已安装的vllm版本）"

msgid ""
"If you need to customize the profiling points, it is highly recommended to "
"copy a symbol configuration file to your working directory and point to it "
"with the `PROFILING_SYMBOLS_PATH` environment variable."
msgstr "如果需要自定义分析点，强烈建议将符号配置文件复制到工作目录，并通过`PROFILING_SYMBOLS_PATH`环境变量指向该文件。"

msgid "##### Configuration file updates"
msgstr "##### 配置文件更新"

msgid ""
"After you change profiling symbols, restart the vLLM service so the updated "
"configuration file is loaded."
msgstr "更改分析符号后，请重启vLLM服务以加载更新后的配置文件。"

msgid "##### Field Descriptions"
msgstr "##### 字段说明"

msgid "##### Configuration Examples"
msgstr "##### 配置示例"

msgid "- Example 1: Custom handler"
msgstr "- 示例1：自定义处理器"

msgid "- Example 2: Default timer"
msgstr "- 示例2：默认计时器"

msgid "- Example 3: Version constraint"
msgstr "- 示例3：版本约束"

msgid "##### Custom Attribute Collection"
msgstr "##### 自定义属性收集"

msgid ""
"The `attributes` field supports flexible custom attribute collection and "
"allows operations and transformations on function arguments and return "
"values."
msgstr "`attributes`字段支持灵活的自定义属性收集，并允许对函数参数和返回值进行操作和转换。"

msgid "###### Basic Syntax"
msgstr "###### 基本语法"

msgid ""
"- Argument access: use the parameter name directly, e.g., `input_ids`\n"
"- Return value access: use the `return` keyword\n"
"- Pipeline operations: use `|` to chain multiple operations\n"
"- Attribute access: use `attr` to access object attributes"
msgstr ""
"- 参数访问：直接使用参数名，例如 `input_ids`\n"
"- 返回值访问：使用 `return` 关键字\n"
"- 管道操作：使用 `|` 链接多个操作\n"
"- 属性访问：使用 `attr` 访问对象属性"

msgid "###### Example"
msgstr "###### 示例"

msgid "###### Expression Notes"
msgstr "###### 表达式说明"

msgid ""
"1. `len(input_ids)`: get the length of parameter `input_ids`.\n"
"2. `len(return) | str`: get the length of the return value and convert to string (equivalent to `str(len(return))`).\n"
"3. `return[0] | attr input_ids | len`: get the length of the `input_ids` attribute of the first element in the return value."
msgstr ""
"1. `len(input_ids)`：获取参数 `input_ids` 的长度。\n"
"2. `len(return) | str`：获取返回值的长度并转换为字符串（相当于 `str(len(return))`）。\n"
"3. `return[0] | attr input_ids | len`：获取返回值中第一个元素的 `input_ids` 属性的长度。"

msgid "###### Supported Expression Types"
msgstr "###### 支持的表达式类型"

msgid ""
"- Basic operations: `len()`, `str()`, `int()`, `float()`\n"
"- Index access: `return[0]`, `return['key']`\n"
"- Attribute access: `return | attr attr_name`\n"
"- Pipeline composition: chain operations with `|`"
msgstr ""
"- 基本操作：`len()`、`str()`、`int()`、`float()`\n"
"- 索引访问：`return[0]`、`return['key']`\n"
"- 属性访问：`return | attr attr_name`\n"
"- 管道组合：使用 `|` 链式操作"

msgid "###### Advanced Examples"
msgstr "###### 高级示例"

msgid "##### Custom Handler"
msgstr "##### 自定义处理器"

msgid ""
"When `handler` specifies a custom function, it must match the following "
"signature:"
msgstr "当 `handler` 指定自定义函数时，必须符合以下签名："

msgid ""
"If the custom handler fails to import, the system will automatically fall "
"back to the default timer mode."
msgstr "如果自定义处理器导入失败，系统将自动回退到默认的计时器模式。"

msgid "## Ascend PyTorch Profiler"
msgstr "## Ascend PyTorch 性能分析器"

msgid "### 0. Installation and Configuration"
msgstr "### 0. 安装与配置"

msgid ""
"No additional packages need to be installed; it can be enabled through "
"command-line configuration. Currently, vLLM enables **python stack** by "
"default, which can significantly inflate the collected performance data. If "
"you do not wish to collect **python stack**, you can disable it using "
"`torch_profiler_with_stack=false`."
msgstr ""
"无需安装额外软件包，可通过命令行配置启用。当前 vLLM 默认启用 **python stack**，这可能会显著增加采集的性能数据量。如果不需要采集 "
"**python stack**，可以使用 `torch_profiler_with_stack=false` 禁用它。"

msgid "### 1. Preparation for Collection"
msgstr "### 1. 采集前准备"

msgid ""
"Start the online service and set the `--profiler-config` parameter to "
"control the path for saving performance files. After the parameter is set, "
"the collection function is enabled."
msgstr "启动在线服务，并设置 `--profiler-config` 参数以控制性能文件的保存路径。设置该参数后，采集功能即被启用。"

msgid ""
"> Note:**January 19, 2026: The vLLM mainline has deprecated the "
"VLLM_TORCH_PROFILER_DIR environment variable.**[Related "
"PR](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/5928)  When using the "
"vLLM Ascend mainline code to collect profiler data, remember to use the "
"`--profiler-config` (online) parameter or the `profiler_config` (offline) "
"parameter."
msgstr ""
"> 注意：**2026年1月19日：vLLM 主线已弃用 VLLM_TORCH_PROFILER_DIR 环境变量。**[相关 "
"PR](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/5928) 使用 vLLM Ascend "
"主线代码采集 profiler 数据时，请记得使用 `--profiler-config`（在线）参数或 "
"`profiler_config`（离线）参数。"

msgid "### 2. Start Collection"
msgstr "### 2. 开始采集"

msgid ""
"Performance collection is controlled by sending API requests. You can start "
"collection after stabilizing the actual business data and collect profiling "
"for a few seconds before stopping; or you can start collection first, then "
"send business requests, and finally stop."
msgstr "性能采集通过发送 API 请求来控制。可以在实际业务数据稳定后开始采集，采集几秒后停止；也可以先开始采集，再发送业务请求，最后停止。"

msgid "Send the following request to start the profiling service:"
msgstr "发送以下请求以启动性能分析服务："

msgid "Send the following request to stop the profiling service:"
msgstr "发送以下请求以停止性能分析服务："

msgid ""
"Send requests according to your actual business data. After sending the "
"requests, stop the profiling service, and the data will be automatically "
"saved to the previously configured path:"
msgstr "根据实际业务数据发送请求。发送请求后，停止性能分析服务，数据将自动保存到之前配置的路径："

msgid "### 4. Analyze Data"
msgstr "### 4. 分析数据"

msgid ""
"Navigate to the `./vllm_profile` directory and locate the generated "
"`*ascend_pt` folder. This folder needs to be analyzed before profiling data "
"can be examined."
msgstr ""
"进入 `./vllm_profile` 目录，找到生成的 `*ascend_pt` 文件夹。需要先对该文件夹进行分析，才能查看性能分析数据。"

msgid ""
"After analysis, the `*ascend_pt` directory will contain many files, with the"
" main analysis focus being the `ASCEND_PROFILER_OUTPUT` folder. This "
"directory will include the following files:"
msgstr ""
"分析完成后，`*ascend_pt` 目录下会包含许多文件，主要分析关注点为 `ASCEND_PROFILER_OUTPUT` "
"文件夹。该目录将包含以下文件："

msgid "- `analysis.db`: Performance data in database format"
msgstr "- `analysis.db`：数据库格式的性能数据"

msgid "- `api_statistic.csv`: API call statistics"
msgstr "- `api_statistic.csv`：API 调用统计"

msgid "- `ascend_pytorch_profiler_0.db`: Performance data in database format"
msgstr "- `ascend_pytorch_profiler_0.db`：数据库格式的性能数据"

msgid "- `kernel_details.csv`: Kernel-level related data"
msgstr "- `kernel_details.csv`：内核级相关数据"

msgid "- `operator_details.csv`: Operator-level related data"
msgstr "- `operator_details.csv`：算子级相关数据"

msgid "- `op_statistic.csv`: Operator utilization data"
msgstr "- `op_statistic.csv`：算子利用率数据"

msgid "- `step_trace_time.csv`: Scheduling data"
msgstr "- `step_trace_time.csv`：调度数据"

msgid ""
"- `trace_view.json`: Chrome tracing format data, can be opened with "
"[MindStudio "
"Insight](https://www.hiascend.com/document/detail/zh/mindstudio/81RC1/GUI_baseddevelopmenttool/msascendinsightug/Insight_userguide_0002.html)"
msgstr ""
"- `trace_view.json`：Chrome tracing 格式数据，可使用 [MindStudio "
"Insight](https://www.hiascend.com/document/detail/zh/mindstudio/81RC1/GUI_baseddevelopmenttool/msascendinsightug/Insight_userguide_0002.html)"
" 打开"

msgid "| Feature | Ascend PyTorch Profiler | MS Service Profiler |"
msgstr "| 功能 | Ascend PyTorch Profiler | MS Service Profiler |"

msgid "| Parameter | Description | Required |"
msgstr "| 参数 | 描述 | 是否必填 |"

msgid "| Field | Description | Example |"
msgstr "| 字段 | 描述 | 示例 |"

msgid ""
"| Installation Method | Built-in, no additional installation required | "
"Requires building msserviceprofiler from source |"
msgstr "| 安装方式 | 内置，无需额外安装 | 需要从源码构建 msserviceprofiler |"

msgid ""
"| Collection Granularity | PyTorch operator level | Service framework "
"function level |"
msgstr "| 采集粒度 | PyTorch 算子级别 | 服务框架函数级别 |"

msgid "| Control Method | API request control | Configuration file control |"
msgstr "| 控制方式 | API 请求控制 | 配置文件控制 |"

msgid ""
"| Applicable Scenarios | Model operator performance analysis | Service "
"framework workflow analysis |"
msgstr "| 适用场景 | 模型算子性能分析 | 服务框架工作流分析 |"

msgid "| Data Format | ascend_pt format | Chrome Tracing + CSV |"
msgstr "| 数据格式 | ascend_pt 格式 | Chrome Tracing + CSV |"

msgid ""
"| Main Advantage | Operator-level performance analysis | Service framework "
"workflow visualization |"
msgstr "| 主要优势 | 算子级性能分析 | 服务框架工作流可视化 |"

msgid ""
"| Supported Collection Capabilities | PyTorch operator level | PyTorch "
"operator level and Service framework function level |"
msgstr "| 支持的采集能力 | PyTorch 算子级别 | PyTorch 算子级别和服务框架函数级别 |"

msgid ""
"| enable | Switch for profiling: <br />0: disable<br />1: enable<br "
"/>Default: 0 | Yes |"
msgstr "| enable | 性能分析开关：<br />0：关闭<br />1：开启<br />默认值：0 | 是 |"

msgid ""
"| prof_dir | Directory to store collected performance data. <br />Default: "
"`${HOME}/.ms_server_profiler` | No |"
msgstr ""
"| prof_dir | 存储采集的性能数据的目录。<br />默认值：`${HOME}/.ms_server_profiler` | 否 |"

msgid ""
"| profiler_level | Data collection level. Default is \"INFO\" (normal "
"level). | No |"
msgstr "| profiler_level | 数据采集级别。默认值为 \"INFO\"（正常级别）。 | 否 |"

msgid ""
"| acl_task_time | Switch to collect operator dispatch latency and execution "
"latency. Values: <br />0: off. Default; 0 or any invalid value means off.<br"
" />1: on. When enabled, calls `aclprofCreateConfig` with "
"`ACL_PROF_TASK_TIME_L0`.<br />2: on. MSPTI-based dump. When enabled, set "
"before starting the service: `export "
"LD_PRELOAD={INSTALL_DIR}/lib64/libmspti.so`, where `{INSTALL_DIR}` is the "
"CANN installation root (e.g. `/usr/local/Ascend/cann` for a typical root "
"install).<br />3: on. Torch Profiler–based dump. | No |"
msgstr ""
"| acl_task_time | 采集算子调度延迟和执行延迟的开关。取值：<br />0：关闭。默认值；0 或任何无效值表示关闭。<br "
"/>1：开启。开启时，使用 `ACL_PROF_TASK_TIME_L0` 调用 `aclprofCreateConfig`。<br />2：开启。基于"
" MSPTI 的转储。开启时，在启动服务前设置：`export "
"LD_PRELOAD={INSTALL_DIR}/lib64/libmspti.so`，其中 `{INSTALL_DIR}` 是 CANN "
"安装根目录（例如典型根安装的 `/usr/local/Ascend/cann`）。<br />3：开启。基于 Torch Profiler 的转储。 |"
" 否 |"

msgid ""
"| acl_prof_task_time_level | Profiling level and duration. Values: <br />L0:"
" collect operator dispatch and execution latency only; lower overhead (no "
"operator basic info).<br />L1: collect AscendCL interface performance "
"(host–device and inter-device sync/async memory copy latencies), plus "
"operator dispatch, execution, and basic info for comprehensive analysis.<br "
"/>`{time}`: optional duration segment; integer 1–999, unit seconds.<br />If "
"unset, defaults to L0 until program exit; invalid values fall back to "
"defaults.<br />Level and duration can be combined, e.g., "
"`\"acl_prof_task_time_level\": \"L1;10\"`.<br />**Note:** When Torch "
"Profiler is used (`acl_task_time` set to `3`), `{time}` duration is not "
"supported. | No |"
msgstr ""
"| acl_prof_task_time_level | 性能分析级别和持续时间。取值：<br "
"/>L0：仅采集算子调度和执行延迟；开销较低（无算子基本信息）。<br />L1：采集 AscendCL 接口性能（主机-"
"设备和设备间同步/异步内存拷贝延迟），以及算子调度、执行和基本信息，用于全面分析。<br />`{time}`：可选的持续时间段；整数 "
"1–999，单位秒。<br />如果未设置，默认为 L0 直到程序退出；无效值回退到默认值。<br />级别和持续时间可以组合，例如 "
"`\"acl_prof_task_time_level\": \"L1;10\"`。<br />**注意：** 使用 Torch Profiler "
"时（`acl_task_time` 设置为 `3`），不支持 `{time}` 持续时间。 | 否 |"

msgid ""
"| timelimit | Profiling duration for the service. The process stops "
"automatically after this time. Range: integer 0–7200, unit: seconds. Default"
" 0 means unlimited. Recommend at least 120 s; shorter runs may lack data for"
" parsed outputs and trigger warnings. | No |"
msgstr ""
"| timelimit | 服务的性能分析持续时间。进程在此时间后自动停止。范围：整数 0–7200，单位：秒。默认值 0 表示无限制。建议至少 120"
" 秒；运行时间过短可能导致解析输出数据不足并触发警告。 | 否 |"

msgid ""
"| domain | Limit profiling to the specified domains to reduce data volume. "
"String, separated by semicolons, case-sensitive, e.g., \"Request; "
"KVCache\".<br />Empty means all available domains.<br />Available domains: "
"Request, KVCache, ModelExecute, BatchSchedule, Communication.<br />Note: If "
"the selected domains are incomplete, analysis output may show warnings due "
"to missing data. See [Reference Table "
"1](https://www.hiascend.com/document/detail/zh/canncommercial/850/devaids/Profiling/mindieprofiling_0010.html)."
" | No |"
msgstr ""
"| domain | 将性能分析限制在指定域以减少数据量。字符串，以分号分隔，区分大小写，例如 \"Request; KVCache\"。<br "
"/>空字符串表示所有可用域。<br />可用域：Request, KVCache, ModelExecute, BatchSchedule, "
"Communication。<br />注意：如果所选域不完整，分析输出可能因缺少数据而显示警告。请参见 [参考表 "
"1](https://www.hiascend.com/document/detail/zh/canncommercial/850/devaids/Profiling/mindieprofiling_0010.html)。"
" | 否 |"

msgid ""
"| torch_prof_stack | Collect operator call stacks (framework and CPU "
"operators). Values: `false` (default, off), `true` (on). Requires "
"`acl_task_time` set to `3`. **Note:** Enabling this configuration introduces"
" additional performance overhead. | No |"
msgstr ""
"| torch_prof_stack | 采集算子调用栈（框架和 CPU 算子）。取值：`false`（默认，关闭），`true`（开启）。需要将 "
"`acl_task_time` 设置为 `3`。**注意：** 开启此配置会引入额外的性能开销。 | 否 |"

msgid ""
"| torch_prof_step_num | Torch Profiler step limit. Integer ≥ 0. Default `0` "
"means collect all steps.<br />Requires `acl_task_time` set to `3`. | No |"
msgstr ""
"| torch_prof_step_num | Torch Profiler 步数限制。整数 ≥ 0。默认值 `0` 表示采集所有步骤。<br "
"/>需要将 `acl_task_time` 设置为 `3`。 | 否 |"

msgid ""
"| profiler_step_num | Step limit for operator and service framework "
"profiling. Integer ≥ 0.<br />`0` or invalid values stop the entire service "
"profiling process.<br />The number of steps actually recorded depends on "
"`modelRunnerExec` events. | No |"
msgstr ""
"| profiler_step_num | 算子和服务框架性能分析的步数限制。整数 ≥ 0。<br />`0` "
"或无效值会停止整个服务性能分析过程。<br />实际记录的步数取决于 `modelRunnerExec` 事件。 | 否 |"

msgid ""
"| symbol | Python import path + attribute chain | "
"`\"vllm.v1.core.kv_cache_manager:KVCacheManager.free\"` |"
msgstr ""
"| symbol | Python 导入路径 + 属性链 | "
"`\"vllm.v1.core.kv_cache_manager:KVCacheManager.free\"` |"

msgid ""
"| handler | Handler type | `\"timer\"` (default) or `\"pkg.mod:func\"` "
"(custom) |"
msgstr "| handler | 处理器类型 | `\"timer\"`（默认）或 `\"pkg.mod:func\"`（自定义） |"

msgid "| domain | Domain tag | `\"KVCache\"`, `\"ModelExecute\"` |"
msgstr "| domain | 域标签 | `\"KVCache\"`, `\"ModelExecute\"` |"

msgid "| name | Event name | `\"EngineCoreExecute\"` |"
msgstr "| name | 事件名称 | `\"EngineCoreExecute\"` |"

msgid "| min_version | Minimum supported vLLM version | `\"0.9.1\"` |"
msgstr "| min_version | 支持的最低 vLLM 版本 | `\"0.9.1\"` |"

msgid "| max_version | Maximum supported vLLM version | `\"0.11.0\"` |"
msgstr "| max_version | 支持的最高 vLLM 版本 | `\"0.11.0\"` |"

msgid ""
"| attributes | Custom attribute collection | Only supported for `\"timer\"` "
"handler. See the section below |"
msgstr "| attributes | 自定义属性采集 | 仅支持 `\"timer\"` 处理器。请参见以下章节 |"
